data.description: A Diamond in the Rough Awaits Your Magic Touch! Are you searching for more than just a house? Do you see beauty where others see despair? Do you have the heart of a creator and the vision of a restorer? Look no further. This residence whispers tales of yesteryear's and beckons for a loving touch. Each creaking floorboard is a verse of an unwritten song, each peeling paint layer a testament to the passage of time, and within these venerable walls lies an unpolished gem waiting for rebirth. We invite you to take a walk through this house — not just as a structure, but as a narrative waiting for its next chapter. With every step, envision the laughter, the warmth, the future you can build here. The property requires a full-scale renovation, offering the perfect canvas for modernization.
